********************************************
**************  gTaskmanager  **************
********************************************

gTaskmanager is a small taskmanager based on GTK+. You'll need at
least gtk v.2.8 to use this program.

gTaskmanager is a fork of xfce4-taskmanager, whithout any xfce
depensencies.

You can check for new releases at http://oliwer.net. Please send 
bug reports to Olivier Duclos <oliwer@free.fr>.


** Building **

./configure
make
make install (as root)

** Usage **

Run 'gtaskmanager'
